Join Our Newsletter
Have Questions? Let Us Know!
Contact Laugh Out Lounge! We have all the answers!
|  Contact Us |
You can email us or find us on Facebook or Instagram. We frequently answer our messages and emails within a few hours.
Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)
What is your refund policy?
Is there an age limit?
What time do doors open?
Do you serve food?
Is there a drink minimum?
All sales are final. There are absolutely no refunds.
All shows are 21+ unless otherwise posted.
Doors typically open one hour before posted showtime.
We do not serve dinner, but we do have snacks like popcorn, chips, and candy.
A two item minimum  is enforced at all shows. Soda, Snacks, and Adult Beverages count toward your minimum. Bottled water does not count toward the minimum. A $10 ticket addendum will apply to anyone in your party who does not meet the minimum.
Where are we located?
Our address is 19 3rd Street NW in the heart of downtown Winter Haven, FL. Use the map below to find us on your GPS.
